  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Located in the stunning landscapes of Engelberg, Hotel Terrace is the true embodiment of alpine elegance and charm. With its prime location overlooking the majestic Swiss Alps, a ski holiday in this hotel offers you a unique blend of tranquillity and adventure.</span></p>
<h2>Skiing couldn't be easier</h2>
<p>A lift pass is included with your stay at the Hotel Terrace, you'll get an Engelberg area lift pass included so you can really make the most of the mountains and what they have to offer.</p>
<h2>Food and drink </h2>
<p>Enjoy dining in the charming alpine restaurant Hotel Terrace has to offer. The <span>Belle Epoque restaurant is warm and sophisticated with large panoramic windows that supply some amazing views of the Swiss peaks. </span><span>Whether it's a hearty breakfast to start your day or an intimate dinner to round it off, the restaurant is a haven for food enthusiasts using locally sourced ingredients through a range of traditional Swiss and international dishes. A</span><span> visit to the hotels Porticos Bar, which has the largest selection of gins in Switzerland, is the perfect end to your evening.</span></p>
<h2><span>Family friendly hotel</span></h2>
<p>After a day of exploring the Titlis mountain, soothe any achy ski legs in the panoramic sauna and enjoy incredible views over the snowy mountain peaks. Hotel Terrace is not just a destination for adults but it's a place where families can create memories together with the fantastic facilities they have on offer. We're sure the children will love the designated play area, with older children making the most of the well-equipped games room. And for those of you with younger infants, the hotel provides all the necessities for a stress free trip, including cots and high chairs, all free of charge. Not to mention the attentive staff at Hotel Terrace are always on hand to assist with any family needs, big or small.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
