  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p><span>Surrounded by the breath-taking views of the Swiss Alps, Hotel Terrace offers you the best of both worlds - the buzz of Engelberg's village and the beauty of the resorts nature. The spa facilities in the hotel offer moments of relaxation, available on a half board basis, the restaurant invites you to taste artistic culinary whilst enjoying panoramic views and the prime location allows you to make the most of everything the resort and ski area has to offer. </span></p>]]></listingDescription>
