  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li><span>Hotel Terrace is about a five minutes' walk from the centre of resort (500 metres) and 1 kilometre from the ski lifts and ski school meeting area. </span></li>
<li><span>The train station is around 800 metres (ten minutes walk) from the hotel.  A shuttle service may be provided on request (subject to availability). The Hotel Terrace funicular lift will take you up to the hotel.</span></li>
<li><span>The ski bus stop is located 300 metres from the hotel at the base of the hotel Funicular. </span><span>The free ski bus runs throughout the winter season connects the village to the train station and valley stations. T</span><span>he bus stop is located near to the base station of the funicular. </span></li>
</ul>
<p>Guests staying in Engelberg will catch the train from Zurich Airport, it takes approx 2hours 15 minutes with one change at Luzern. On arrival into resort a shuttle service will take you to the Hotel Terrace funicular. </p>]]></locationDescription>
