  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Austrian twin rooms </strong>are 17 m²and sleep two people. These rooms have Austrian twin beds, a shower room with WC and a small balcony.</p>
<p><span><strong>Comfort Austrian twin rooms </strong>are 18 m² and sleep two people. These rooms have extra long Austrian twin beds and a shower room with a rain shower as well as a WC with bidet function. They also have dimmable lighting, blackout curtains and USB charging stations by the beds. </span></p>
<p><strong>Room facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities </li>
<li>32" flat-screen TV with English speaking channels </li>
<li>Radio via TV</li>
<li>Telephone </li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi </li>
<li>Safe </li>
<li>All rooms can fit a cot free of charge upon request </li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
